algebra}), by which we mean the algebra whose domain is the Cartesian product \af{Œ†}~\ab
i~Íûâ~\ab I~\af{,}~\aof{ùîª[~\ab{ùíú}~\ab i~]} of the domains of the algebras in \ab{ùíú}, and
