\ab{f} is a \ab J-ary operation symbol and if
\ab a~:~\af{Œ†}~\ab i~Íûâ~\ab I~\af{,}~\ab J~\as{‚Üí}~\aof{ùîª[~\ab{ùíú}~\ab i~]} is, for each
