(\ab{f}~\af{ÃÇ}~\af{‚®Ö}~\ab{ùíú}) \ab a := \as{Œª}~(\ab i~:~\ab I)~\as{‚Üí}
(\ab{f}~\af{ÃÇ}~\ab{ùíú}~\ab i)(\ab{a}~\ab i).\\[8pt]
