A \defn{homomorphism} (or ``hom'') from
\ab{ùë®} to \ab{ùë©} is a setoid function \ab{h}~:~\aof{ùîª[~\ab{ùë®}~]} \aor{‚ü∂} \aof{ùîª[~\ab{ùë©}~]}
