%Indeed, for each pair \ab p \ab q : \Term{X}, if \ab{ùí¶} \af{‚ä´} \ab p \af{‚âà} \ab
%q, then \ab p and \ab q belong to the same \afld{‚âà}-class, so \ab p and \ab q are
