as \ab h ranges over all homomorphisms from \T{X} to algebras in \ab{ùí¶}.  Thus, \Free{X} \af{‚àà}
\af{P} (\af{S} \ab{ùí¶}) \aof{‚äÜ} \af{S} (\af{P} \ab{ùí¶}).
